source.name: Conference Information Data Service
source.description: Contains bibliographic data for science and technology conference proceedings and conference papers from the Energy Citations Database.  Default request returns first fifteen records.  See Technical Documentation for instructions on obtaining additional records.  This data service allows the downloading of bibliographic records in formats that can be used to load the records into other databases or search tools.  To search the Conference Information database, use the Agency Program Page below.
